TY  - JOUR
TI  - Identification of a Certain Stochastic Structure
AU  - Teicher, Henry
AB  - [The structure X<sub>i</sub> = U<sub>i</sub> + α Ui-1 with the U<sub>i</sub> identically and independently distributed (and X<sub>i</sub> observable) is analyzed with respect to the identifiability of the parameter α and the distribution of U. The so-called linear structural relationship is examined briefly.]
C1  - Full publication date: Apr., 1956
